query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'serverfault')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('amazon-ec2',
'apache-2.4',
'commerce',
'debian',
'domain-name-system',
'entities',
'forms',
'networking',
'nginx',
'php',
'postfix',
'ubuntu',
'users')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000 group by t1.name;
